            <li>Ballon d'Or winner in 1998</li>
            <li>FIFA World Player of the Year (1998, 2000, 2003)</li>
            <li>UEFA Champions League winner as a player (2002) and coach (3 consecutive titles with Real Madrid)</li>
            <li>Famous for his iconic volley goal in the 2002 UEFA Champions League Final</li>
